task.summary: Added method to trim the file extension
Added methods to generate html code
Updated controller to take advantage of new methods in MediaOperations
Added support for IGDB API (Game Information API)
Reworked how the exception are managed
Added comments and minor fixes to Rest service
Minor improvements to result.{media_type}.html and media_{media_type}.html
Added option to filter films by language in media_film.html
Improved Book Search API and media_book.html
Improved Music Search API and media_music.html
Added sorting capability to Music API. Rest Service and media_music.html changed accordingly.
Improved Game Search API and related html pages
